subject: I think I should better forg
body:
I think I should better forget about it and look for someone else. I will ask the Finance company to cancel every arrangement for this transfer that is your name.
I do not see any seriousness in your bid to assist me, first you refused sending your details, that is when I know you were not serious, in any way thanks for wasting my time. Have a nice day.

subject: Re:   I think I should better forg
body:
Hello there! I'm sorry if I gave you the wrong impression earlier. I understand that you may be frustrated, but I assure you that I am serious about helping you. Can we please discuss this further? Maybe there's a misunderstanding that we can clear up.

Best wishes,
Elizabeth
